<idea-plugin>
    <id>com.lanchat.idea-lan-chat</id>
    <name>LAN Chat</name>
    <vendor email="liuyifei@example.com" url="https://github.com/CCweixiao/idea-lan-chat">liuyifei</vendor>

    <description><![CDATA[
    <h2>🚀 LAN Chat - 局域网即时通讯工具</h2>
    
    <p><b>急！需求沟通到一半，企微遭遇外星人攻击，无法发送消息...</b></p>
    <p><b>幸好我有 LAN Chat！助我工作效率倍增，永不掉线！</b></p>
    
    <h3>✨ 核心特性</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>🌐 <b>自动发现</b> - 自动扫描局域网内在线同事</li>
        <li>💬 <b>即时通讯</b> - 文本、图片、文件一键发送</li>
        <li>👥 <b>群组聊天</b> - 创建群聊，团队协作更高效</li>
        <li>🔒 <b>安全可靠</b> - 局域网内点对点传输，数据不外泄</li>
        <li>⚡ <b>轻量高效</b> - 极低资源占用，编码聊天两不误</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h3>🎯 适用场景</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>企业内网环境下的团队协作</li>
        <li>远程办公时的快速沟通</li>
        <li>临时网络故障时的备用通讯方案</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p><i>💡 提示：插件启动后会自动扫描局域网内的在线用户</i></p>
    ]]></description>

    <change-notes><![CDATA[
    <h2>1.0.2</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>🎨 优化聊天界面，新增输入框</li>
        <li>🔍 新增局域网IP显示</li>
        <li>👤 支持手动添加联系人</li>
        <li>🖼️ 更换插件图标</li>
        <li>💎 美化发送按钮</li>
    </ul>
    ]]></change-notes>

    <depends>com.intellij.modules.platform</depends>

    <extensions defaultExtensionNs="com.intellij">
        <toolWindow id="LAN Chat"
                    icon="/META-INF/icons/avatar.svg"
                    anchor="right"
                    secondary="true"
                    factoryClass="com.lanchat.ui.LanChatToolWindowFactory"/>
        
        <applicationService serviceImplementation="com.lanchat.LanChatService"/>
        
        <applicationConfigurable parentId="tools"
                                 instance="com.lanchat.ui.settings.LanChatSettingsConfigurable"
                                 id="com.lanchat.settings"
                                 displayName="LAN Chat"/>
    </extensions>

    <actions>
        <action id="com.lanchat.SendFileAction"
                class="com.lanchat.ui.actions.SendFileAction"
                text="Send File"
                description="Send a file to selected contact">
            <add-to-group group-id="ToolsMenu" anchor="last"/>
        </action>
    </actions>
</idea-plugin>
